"2 cups thinly sliced pickling cucumber (about 2 cucumbers)","1 cup thinly sliced Vidalia or other sweet onion","1/2 cup cider vinegar","1/4 cup sugar","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon mustard seeds","4  garlic cloves, minced","2  whole dried red chiles","16  (1/4-inch-thick) slices tomato","1/8 teaspoon salt","1/8 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper"